MNUMBER 96
NAME eagle
*DESCRIPTION_START
You see a large avine with a brownish black body and snow white head, neck and tail. Its piercing black eyes look at you with no comprehension from behind its yellow beak. Its powerful talons are tucked up into its feathers as it glides easily on the wind.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ATTACK1 40
AVINE
BODY 40
DEFENSE 60
SKINADJ 773
SKINITEM 513 25 100
SKINITEM 517 50 200
speed 2
STRATEGY 30
TEX1 An eagle makes a sharp cry.
TEX2 An eagle glides glides in the breeze.
TEX3 An eagle soars magestically among the clouds.
TEXD screeches horribly and begins to spin.
TEXE An eagle swoops in.
TEXF An eagle dives
TEXG An eagle dives in from above.
TEXM An eagle soars
WEAPON 279
;
MNUMBER 205
NAME deer
ANIMAL
BODY 105
ATTACK1 50
DEFENSE 25
STRATEGY 250
WEAPON 1975 -1 20
ARMOR 10
SKINADJ 729
SKINITEM 1974 50 0 0 0
SPEED 2
*DESCRIPTION_START
This magnificent creature of the woods fills your soul with the desire for
the hunt. It looks at you with some apprehension and looks ready to bolt
at any instant.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
;
; MLIST <mlist> <mnum> <ratio> <max #>
;
MLIST 35 8 4 2 ; falcon
MLIST 35 9 100 5 ; sparrow
MLIST 35 10 2 1 ; owl
MLIST 35 96 1 1 ; eagle
MLIST 35 205 10 3 ; deer


